19 const pose_ptr CarModel::getUpdate(const int newSteering, const int newSpeed, const ros::Time& time){
20  timeStep = (time-lastUpdate).toSec();
21  lastUpdate = time;
22  double ds = velocity * timeStep;
23  double oldYaw = pose[2];
24  pose = fwdKin.getUpdate(fwdKin.degToRad(steeringAngle), ds);
